        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">I headed into Nurga to do some exploring and I found the Spiders and the sleeping Ogre.  I tried a few pulls to test out the area and could not come up with a safe way to do this.  Could someone give me some instructions on pulling these safely?  Do I set up in the Ogre room?  Do I fear kite?  Any information would be great!!</P><P>Thank you and</P><P>Evilhugs <img src=icon_smile_evil.gif border=0 align=middle></font></td>
