        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">I was always sloppy when it came to breaking them. Using the EQAtlas map, head thru the goblin area to the spider area. You should find yourself going down a little ramp and in an alcove to your left there should be 2 spiders and another 2 around the corner to your right.<BR>Cast diamondskin, then I would root one and blast the other with Asy and VOS and pet/tap. When the other one makes a nuisance of himself I would ST until I was ready to take it. Never tried fear-kiting, just root/dot and pet would clean them up with about a third health left.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
